name: scriptbench

scripts.dev: fse copy serve.project.json default.project.json && rbxtsc && concurrently "rbxtsc -w" "rojo serve"
scripts.build: fse copy build.project.json default.project.json && rbxtsc && rojo build --output Scriptbench.rbxm
scripts.plugin: fse copy build.project.json default.project.json && rbxtsc && rojo build --plugin Scriptbench.rbxm

author: AsynchronousAI
description: Roblox plugin to compare your scripts with graphs, tables, and a microprofiler!
